      <title>Three ceramic reliefs. I used the ceramic reliefs to try to find a way of combin...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DV8LKGsDebD/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/653936562_18434451622139640_23203757184433175_n.webp?stp=dst-webp_p1080x1080_sh2.08&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NDAwMTYyMjI0MjY0MDc3NA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTYyMi5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=DT-roQssSicQ7kNvwFM4c0n&amp;_nc_oc=AdqFcy-8LxGfyCC9K2x3qr4SOhELIIOjzOlZNSdG6o9YtHbbhl43BHUu5ZcF2Fcopgw&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=bM92lurzxW_UJ4p8V3INuA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzHtSemx4ZWBqrZQaYvynJK0AwJSq-w1BTIc-lllnPevw&amp;oe=69C99CCD" alt="Instagram billede fra @petopaj" /></p><p><strong>@petopaj</strong></p><p>Three ceramic reliefs. I used the ceramic reliefs to try to find a way of combining smaller stories into one work. Have them talk to each other in all directions. It&#x27;s now slowly working its way into my paintings which was everything I hoped for. More on this later. But for now I will enjoy the process <br/>
<br/>
These are available at @bricksgallery_cph</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/653936562_18434451622139640_23203757184433175_n.webp?stp=dst-webp_p1080x1080_sh2.08&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1NDAwMTYyMjI0MjY0MDc3NA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTYyMi5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=DT-roQssSicQ7kNvwFM4c0n&amp;_nc_oc=AdqFcy-8LxGfyCC9K2x3qr4SOhELIIOjzOlZNSdG6o9YtHbbhl43BHUu5ZcF2Fcopgw&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=bM92lurzxW_UJ4p8V3INuA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzHtSemx4ZWBqrZQaYvynJK0AwJSq-w1BTIc-lllnPevw&amp;oe=69C99CCD" alt="Instagram billede fra @petopaj" /></p><p><strong>@petopaj</strong></p><p>Three ceramic reliefs. I used the ceramic reliefs to try to find a way of combining smaller stories into one work. Have them talk to each other in all directions. It&#x27;s now slowly working its way into my paintings which was everything I hoped for. More on this later. But for now I will enjoy the process <br/>
<br/>
These are available at @bricksgallery_cph</p>]]></content:encoded>
